descriptionHtml:
Did you know, in 2020, companies around the world spend a total of US$ 336 billion on digital media ads? One of the main reasons why major brands do so is because they want to increase their brand value, which would translate into more revenue. Companies are doing so even before their first sale is made.

Since increasing media exposure would result in an increase in value, what is stopping you from increasing media exposure for your home and/or properties you own? With Clicks™, you can do so for FREE! On top of that, you get to take part in our weekly campaigns and stand a chance to win cash prizes!

Visit our official Facebook page to look out for the latest details of weekly campaigns: https://www.facebook.com/www.clicks.sg

title: Clicks

creator: Clicks.sg
descriptionHtml:
Clicks® is a Singapore startup (UEN: 20211765Z) and we are creating the "LinkedIn" for real estate. In doing so, we strive to digitalise the real estate industry, reduce friction in real estate transactions and make real estate transactions more cost efficient.

On top of offering free property listing services for properties in Singapore, Malaysia, Thailand, Indonesia and Australia and facilitating the buy/sell/rent process, we also aim to create an ecosystem that allows tenants, property owners, agents and people in the real estate related industries to connect with each other. With this ecosystem, we will create economic opportunities for everyone in the real estate related industries.

Some of our most popular features (all are FREE to use) include:
• Clickstimate – an estimated valuation of your HDB and condos in Singapore.
• NEW digital, smart contract for HDB rentals in Singapore.
• Property listings for residential properties in Singapore, Malaysia, Thailand, Indonesia and Australia.
• Refresh your listings so they will always stay at the top of the page and gather a large number of views.
• Connect and contact with others securely with our networking feature.
• Property Virtual Profiles (PVP) – create a PVP to:
o revisit your previous homes and the memories you have made in them through videos, images and even VR Tours
o archive precious moments spent in your current home
o plan for your future dream home
descriptionShort: Increase your property's media exposure with Clicks™!
